caller_intent: The caller (John) wants to remove a Hyundai from his insurance policy and add a 2025 Subaru, following up on a previous voicemail.
resolution_steps: Agent Allison confirms the caller's request to remove the Hyundai and add the 2025 Subaru.
Agent assures the caller the change will be processed immediately.
Agent mentions sending updated policy documents via email.
knowledge_required: Email communication protocols for policy updates
summary: John contacted Alliance Insurance to adjust his policy by removing a Hyundai and adding a 2025 Subaru. Agent Allison confirmed the change and committed to sending updated documents via email. The conversation concluded with mutual agreement on the next steps.
